title: People Holding Hands Dark Skin Tone Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a couple or friends holding hands, with one person having a dark skin tone and the other a medium-light skin tone. It signifies connection, unity, and relationships.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the 'people holding hands' emoji with dark and medium-light skin tones presents a warm and inclusive image of connection. The hands are rendered with Apple's signature soft, rounded edges and a subtle 3D sheen, suggesting a gentle, reassuring grasp. The smooth gradients and realistic lighting enhance the feeling of unity and partnership, making it perfect for expressing friendship, romance, or solidarity.
